## What Makes Hub-and-Spoke Architecture Effective?

Comprehensive hub pages covering broad topics link to detailed spoke pages addressing specific subtopics. This allows concentrated signals, logical user journeys, and scalable expansion.

## Where Should Internal Links Point?

**Core conversion pages** receive links from all relevant outer content.

**Authority hubs** aggregate links from related spoke pages.

**Related content** connects horizontally between peer pages.

**Orphan pages** with valuable content receive strategic connections.

## What Results Can I Expect from Internal Linking?

Internal linking improvements typically show ranking impacts within 4-12 weeks. Pages receiving concentrated linking attention often gain 3-10 position improvements for target queries.
